title: Bonus: Michael Moore In New York
description:
In this bonus episode of the Late Night Podcast, Michael Moore speaks with Late Night producer Henry Melcher as Moore travels from the Late Night green room to backstage at his Broadway show, "The Terms of My Surrender."
